==Norwegian==
===Pronoun===
[[Category:Norwegian pronouns]]
'''det'''
#[[it]]; third person singular, neuter gender. Nominative, accusative or dative. (genitive: see [[dets]])
===Demonstrative pronoun===
'''det''' {{n}}
#[[that]]
===Definite article===
'''det''' {{n}}
#[[the]]; only used if there is an adjective in front of the noun.
#:'''Example'''
#:''[[huset]]'' - the house
#:'''''det''' røde huset'' - the red house
===Related words===
*[[den]]
*[[de]]
*[[dem]]

